item.description:
This primary market research project sought to gain insights and answers from the research question,&ldquo;How does digitalization affect the visitor engagement at museums?&rdquo;
The main purpose was to contribute to the client&rsquo;s (OMA) 2025 digitization strategy for museums in Ontario. Contributions involved developing further insights, supporting and validating assumptions.
This research would help gauge consumer perception about the digitalization of museums and enable us to find opportunities for further improvement &amp; innovation.
